{"tid":453922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲美少女被2名警察性侵","createTime":"2017-10-31T15:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T16:47:04.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8e5d155217e6b47cec54602a1534e046559614","tid":453922,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T15:55:12.000Z","msg":"據英國《每日郵報》28日報道，一名18歲的美國少女狀告兩名紐約緝毒警察在執法期間強奸了她。這位網名為安娜&middot;錢伯斯的少女稱，9月15日晚上，她因為吸食大麻被兩名紐約警察逮捕。令她沒想到的是，當她被拷上手銬押送上警車后，兩名警察居然對她起了歹念。其中一名警察在警車內強奸了她，而另外一人則強迫她為他口交。 <br />\n<br />\n當地時間26號，大陪審團在經過一周的聽證後進行了投票，決定起訴這兩名警察，他們被控犯有一級強姦罪。據報道，兩人將在下周初接受審訊，如果罪名成立，兩人將面臨最少3年，最多25年的有期徒刑。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.cn/sh/2017-10-30/detail-ifynfrfn0183812.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.cn%2Fsh%2F2017-10-30%2Fdetail-ifynfrfn0183812.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=SW0INPOEqdY4XwsDJT1F44zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=5373051a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.cn/sh/2017-10-30/detail-ifynfrfn0183812.d.html?from=wap</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/20171030/ZCxk-fynhhay8308747.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F20171030%2FZCxk-fynhhay8308747.jpg&h=795f137f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/20171030/hrex-fynhhay8308759.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F20171030%2Fhrex-fynhhay8308759.jpg&h=34034b9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd9c30d0304d5358e12a8f39e713b0307328004","tid":453922,"uid":2474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T15:58:57.000Z","msg":"咁正，難怪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6acfad94ba1fe95fc267257dbb4fd090f47fae","tid":453922,"uid":15730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,